<collectionCode box="[866,922,2009,2025]" pageId="6" pageNumber="327">LEVEL</collectionCode>
. — Pentalofos Formation, Aquitanian, lower Miocene. DIAGNOSIS. — A small 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Carpenter" authorityYear="1864" box="[374,506,217,241]" class="Gastropoda" family="Colloniidae" genus="Homalopoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trochida" pageId="7" pageNumber="327" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
